  ('optometrist-moex-02264', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '患者看遠方有12△exo外隱斜位，正融像儲備會聚力為BO: 6/9/6，負融像儲備會聚力為BI: 18/24/21，根 據帕西瓦爾法則（Percival''s criterion），可以用多少的稜鏡度來緩解其症狀？', '["2△BI", "6△BI", "9△BI", "12△BI"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "276817daacd1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5f97e486c625", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02265', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關兩眼不等視弱視的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["通常遠視兩眼不等視弱視（anisometropic amblyopia）較近視者多", "近視型的兩眼不等視弱視差距3.00 D以上就可能發生", "散光型的兩眼不等視弱視差距1.50 D以上就可能發生", "遠視型的兩眼不等視弱視差距2.00 D以上就可能發生"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "276817daacd1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5f97e486c625", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02266', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一位受測者視力檢查結果如下：右眼：+4.00DS/-1.00DC×100視力20/80；左眼：+0.50 DS視力20/20， 最有可能屬於下列那種弱視？', '["斜視性弱視（strabismic amblyopia）", "視覺剝奪性弱視（vision deprivation amblyopia）", "兩眼不等視性弱視（anisometropic amblyopia）", "高度屈光不正性弱視（isometropic amblyopia）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "276817daacd1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5f97e486c625", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
