  ('optometrist-moex-02270', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種現象與弱視（amblyopia）最無相關性？', '["對比敏感度（contrast sensitivity）變差", "擁擠效應（crowding effect）", "夜盲（nyctalopia）", "偏心注視（eccentric fixation）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "276817daacd1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5f97e486c625", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02271', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關最小解析角MAR（minimum angle of resolution），下列敘述何者正確？', '["是能解析最大視標的臨界角度", "是視力值倒數的2倍", "視力6/6 的MAR值是5分角", "視力20/200的logMAR值是1.0"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02272', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關色覺異常（color deficiency）之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["針對先天性色覺異常者，進行石原氏測試（Ishihara color test）可採用雙眼同時檢查", "紅－綠色覺異常者對於紅色、橘色、黃色及綠色容易產生混淆", "罹患先天性紅－綠色覺異常之比例，男性比女性為 8：1", "糖尿病、青光眼、晶體變黃及黃斑部病變皆可能導致後天性色覺異常之發生"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02273', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關散光的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["在孩童身上，順散光（with-the-rule）較常見", "在逆散光（against-the-rule），角膜在水平方向最陡，矯正時應把負圓柱鏡（minus cylinder）鏡軸放在 180度左右", "在順散光，角膜在垂直方向最陡，矯正時應把正圓柱鏡（plus cylinder）鏡軸放在90度左右", "斜散光（oblique astigmatism）代表意義為角膜上最陡的方向不在也不接近 90度或180度"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
